==Logo and colors==
For their inaugural [[American National Rugby League]] season the club adopted the colors of red, white and blue but the home uniforms are predominately red, while the away uniforms are predominantly white.<ref>http://www.amnrl.com/graphx/teamphoto_slayers.jpg</ref> They have a team partnership with the [[St George Illawarra Dragons]] of Australia's [[National Rugby League]] (NRL).<ref name=amnrl>{{cite web |url= http://www.amnrl.com/teams/washington-dc.html|title= Washington D.C. Slayers|author= |date= 2008 |work= amnrl.com |publisher= |accessdate=January 19, 2011}}</ref>

